reviewText: I got this for my 7 year old little brother who is obsessed with goosebumps and he absolutely loved this set of movies! Exactly how I remember them from when I was a kid also! Very pleased!
The DVDs are in great condition, work great, and look great. An awesome bargain for this high quality DVD collection!

I've always loved Goosebumps since I was a kid. Now my son loves them. So needless to say I was extremely happy when I found this & for a good price. Fast shipping, exactly as it was supposed to be. Cant wait to give it to him. Its going to be a birthday present.
